{
  "stem": "21648.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The best, my father used to make a Shabbat.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'll never forget that, [SOBBING] never.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In which way you want to know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The tables, the-- the love from the parents?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They say in the-- from the-- from the books we used to make kiddush and put-- and singing with my father at the table all of the religious songs from the-- from the Bibles.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And of course we had the beautiful dinners, [INAUDIBLE] with everything.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we was not allowed to play outside because rabbi's children.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That would be a disgrace.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But we had a wonderful life, really till Hitler came.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had a wonderful-- I can't, there's not enough time to explain those things.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we used to be invited, of course.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, very much.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A matter of fact, he danced in [INAUDIBLE], yes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But you know after the war everything changed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, when the war began, when Hitler came, what he did in my city in Rowne, the first day when he came he took 500 men, Jewish men, and we had the jail past the city.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he said he's taking them to work and he killed them all, the first morning when we-- when he came to Rowne.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] I guess it was in 1939 or '38, something-- something, like that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I really can't recall.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was home.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We all was home.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was-- we didn't know what he's gonna do.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We think Hitler comes, Germany.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't know it's Hitler, he's coming, and he's going to make just as good as Poland, just as good as Russia.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't understood what is gonna kill Jews.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Can I scratch my nose?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, right away the people saw what was happened.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The women was free.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then later on, the women would have children on their hands.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
